msgctxt "sn45.41:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: 5. Aññatitthiyapeyyālavagga → virāgasuttaṃ (bj) | virāga (pts1)
msgctxt "sn45.41:0.2"
msgid "5. Aññatitthiyapeyyālavagga "
msgstr "5. Abbreviated Texts on Followers of Other Paths "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 41. Rāgavirāgasutta → aññatitthiyavaggo (s1-3) | aññatitthiyapeyyālo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn45.41:0.3"
msgid "41. Rāgavirāgasutta "
msgstr "41. The Fading Away of Greed "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.28, sc1
msgctxt "sn45.41:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.41:1.2"
msgid "“Sace vo, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evaṃ puccheyyuṃ: "
msgstr "“Mendicants, if wanderers who follow another path were to ask you: "

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.3"
msgid "‘kimatthiyaṃ, āvuso, samaṇe gotame brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti, evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ byākareyyātha: "
msgstr "‘Reverends, what’s the purpose of living the spiritual life with the ascetic Gotama?’ You should answer them like this: "

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.4"
msgid "‘rāgavirāgatthaṃ kho, āvuso, bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti. "
msgstr "‘The purpose of living the spiritual life under the Buddha is the fading away of greed.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.41:1.5"
msgid "Sace pana vo, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evaṃ puccheyyuṃ: "
msgstr "If wanderers who follow other paths were to ask you: "

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.6"
msgid "‘atthi panāvuso, maggo, atthi paṭipadā rāgavirāgāyā’ti, evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ byākareyyātha: "
msgstr "‘Is there a path and a practice for the fading away of greed?’ You should answer them like this: "

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.7"
msgid "‘atthi kho, āvuso, maggo, atthi paṭipadā rāgavirāgāyā’ti. "
msgstr "‘There is a path and a practice for the fading away of greed.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.41:1.8"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, maggo, katamā ca paṭipadā rāgavirāgāya? "
msgstr "And what is that path, what is that practice for the fading away of greed? "

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.9"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is: "

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.10"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "

msgctxt "sn45.41:1.11"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, maggo, ayaṃ paṭipadā rāgavirāgāyāti. "
msgstr "This is the path, this is the practice for the fading away of greed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.41:1.12"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ byākareyyāthā”ti. "
msgstr "When questioned by wanderers who follow other paths, that’s how you should answer them.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.41:1.13"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

